history.content:
The Student Association for Applied Statistics (SAAS) is recruiting for the Fall 2020 semester! SAAS is a community of UC Berkeley students with a shared interest in applied statistics. We offer research and consulting projects, workshops, resources, and professional events. We have committees for students of all experience levels and welcome students of all majors.

For Fall 2020, we’re recruiting for 8 committees: Career Exploration, Data Consulting, Education, Insights & Analytics, Research & Publication, Web Development, Events & Marketing (IVP), and Expansionary Action (EVP).

Our application is due on Saturday, September 12 @ 11:59 PM PDT and can be found here: http://tinyurl.com/saasfa20app.

Facebook Recruitment Event: https://www.facebook.com/events/2754193391490609/ 

To learn more about our organization, visit our website at saas.berkeley.edu! Feel free to email us with questions at contact@saas.berkeley.edu.
